In the Matter of ORDER-STATE BAR. No. 71P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Carolin Bakewell, Raleigh, for N.C. State Bar.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th day of January 2005 by Respondent (Edward Brooks) to Compel Enforcement of Mandates of this Court's Orders:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of February 2005."
